x10.matrix

Class Debug

  • x10.lang.Object
    • x10.matrix.Debug

  • public class Debug
extends x10.lang.Object
    This debug tool provides self defined assertion and print methods. In a multi-place execution, print-out of the same place will be display together, after calling flush() method.
